  </header>
  
  <section class="fyre-comment-body">
    <div class="fyre-comment">
      <p><p>Very intersting point of view, far from the rage we've read here and there. I am fascinated by the evolution of what defines ou identity and you are right, this change in Gmail probably doesn't matter much.</p><p><br/></p><p>Incidentally, you've made a very pertinent side point:</p><p>"with content sharing as part of the interaction, rather than a social stream"</p><p><br/></p><p>The (re)emergence of person-to-person platforms (snapchat for instance) partially replacing FB/Twitter posts seems to be trendy...</p></p>
